Two big focus areas at Mist the past weeks.

🕵️No IP Tracking!
The Mist Wallet (and other systems) keep all players anonymous and free!

💯Your Keys, Your Game.
Mist ensures you own your keys, own your items, and own your game. Every Web3 system we have is fully decentralized.
